HEADWORD: Ilion
<hw>Ilion</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>Ilium, or Troy, the ancient city
in Asia Minor that was the site of the Trojan War; -- a variant spelling
of <altname>Ilium</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Troy, Ilium.</syn>⟦br⟧
